text: Warren Grant "Maggie" Magnuson (April 12, 1905 - May 20, 1989) was an American lawyer and politician. He was a member of the Democratic Party. He was a U.S. Representative (1937-1944) and a U.S. Senator (1944-1981) from Washington. ==References== Category:1905 births Category:1989 deaths Category:Lawyers from Seattle Category:United States senators from Washington (state) Category:United States representatives from Washington Category:Deans of the United States Senate Category:Presidents pro tempore of the United States Senate Category:Politicians from Minnesota Category:Politicians from Seattle Category:Democratic Party (United States) politicians Category:Lawyers from Minnesota
